sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant App as Producer App
    participant Ser as KafkaAvroSerializer
    participant Cache as Local Schema Cache
    participant SR as Schema Registry
    participant Broker as Kafka Broker

    App->>Ser: send(Topic, Key, ValueRecord)
    Ser->>Cache: Check if schema exists in local cache
    
    alt Schema exists in Cache (Cache Hit)
        Cache-->>Ser: Return Schema ID (e.g., ID 42)
    else Schema not in Cache (Cache Miss)
        Ser->>SR: POST /subjects/topic-value/versions (Schema JSON)
        SR->>SR: Validate schema compatibility
        SR->>SR: Save schema to _schemas topic
        SR-->>Ser: Return Schema ID (ID 42)
        Ser->>Cache: Save schema details and ID 42 to Cache
    end

    Ser->>Ser: Prepend magic byte (0x00) + Schema ID (ID 42, 4 bytes)
    Ser->>Ser: Serialize payload using Avro schema into binary
    Ser-->>App: Return serialized binary byte array
    App->>Broker: Publish message to Kafka topic
